==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Calibrate
<hw>Cal"i*brate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To ascertain
the caliber of, as of a thermometer tube; also, more generally, to
determine or rectify the graduation of, as of the various standards or
graduated instruments.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Calibration</ent>⟦br⟧
